"&#xa0;\nWritten evidence from \nChief Constable Martin Richards\n QPM\n, Sussex Police\n [PCC Progress 46]\n&#xa0;\nRe: Evidence to the Home Affairs Select Committee&#xa0;Points of Clarification in response to the uncorrected transcript&#xa0;\nIn response to Q241 I wish to add the following to provide a more detailed chronology to assist the Committee. \n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nI was also asked at Q243 how many police information notices has\n Sussex Police issued last year?\n I can confirm that we have recorded two thousand and four (2004) police information notices between 1 January 2013 and 31 December 2013. \n&#xa0;\nI hope this is helpful.\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nMartin RichardsChief Constable\nJanuary 2014\n&#xa0;\n"